name: The Clownfish (Anemonefish)
description:
An illustration of The Clownfish (Anemonefish) in geometric style also known as Lowpoly Art. What is Lowpoly? Lowpoly, simply is a work made of straight lines and angles that form a lot of triangles that create an illustration. 

JPEG file, 4500x4500 pixels, 300dpi sRGB ©2022
